<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_b3055f-dc kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_6f3184-4a"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fas_arrow-alt-circle-right kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M256 8c137 0 248 111 248 248S393 504 256 504 8 393 8 256 119 8 256 8zM140 300h116v70.9c0 10.7 13 16.1 20.5 8.5l114.3-114.9c4.7-4.7 4.7-12.2 0-16.9l-114.3-115c-7.6-7.6-20.5-2.2-20.5 8.5V212H140c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v64c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12z"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Your application has been received.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_65c204-f7"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fas_arrow-alt-circle-right kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M256 8c137 0 248 111 248 248S393 504 256 504 8 393 8 256 119 8 256 8zM140 300h116v70.9c0 10.7 13 16.1 20.5 8.5l114.3-114.9c4.7-4.7 4.7-12.2 0-16.9l-114.3-115c-7.6-7.6-20.5-2.2-20.5 8.5V212H140c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v64c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12z"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Verification has not started.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_58d0a6-80"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fas_arrow-alt-circle-right kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M256 8c137 0 248 111 248 248S393 504 256 504 8 393 8 256 119 8 256 8zM140 300h116v70.9c0 10.7 13 16.1 20.5 8.5l114.3-114.9c4.7-4.7 4.7-12.2 0-16.9l-114.3-115c-7.6-7.6-20.5-2.2-20.5 8.5V212H140c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v64c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12z"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Documents are waiting for review.</span></li>
</ul></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pending status is normal immediately after submission.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column1845_b07c0d-0c"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading1845_d1b756-c0 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading1845_d1b756-c0"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">How Long Does Pending Status Last?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The duration depends on:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_46f807-4a kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_b95112-40"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_disc kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Type of application</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_a08353-be"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_disc kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Number of applications being processed</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_16114d-1c"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_disc kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Verification requirements</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_e00e39-e6"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_disc kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Local Sub Registrar Office workload</span></li>
</ul></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Simple requests may move to Processing within a few days.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column1845_02ade8-e8"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading1845_8bc63c-16 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading1845_8bc63c-16"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">What Does Processing Status Mean?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Processing means that officials are currently reviewing your application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">During this stage:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_df8587-e6 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_4aa8aa-b9"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_send kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Documents are checked.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_5391c9-33"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_send kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Applicant details are verified.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_7e637f-2c"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_send kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Property information is reviewed.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_ff0594-f8"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_send kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Supporting records are examined.</span></li>
</ul></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Processing is a positive sign because it indicates that your application is actively being worked on.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column1845_cee7be-d0"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading1845_052a68-a0 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading1845_052a68-a0"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">What Does Approved Status Mean?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Approved is the status every applicant wants to see.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When an application is approved:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_7b5c50-b1 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_8ab405-e5"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-ic_check kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.41 0l-.69.72-2.78 2.78-.81-.78-.72-.72-1.41 1.41.72.72 1.5 1.5.69.72.72-.72 3.5-3.5.72-.72-1.44-1.41z" transform="translate(0 1)"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Verification is completed.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_945f7f-fd"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-ic_check kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.41 0l-.69.72-2.78 2.78-.81-.78-.72-.72-1.41 1.41.72.72 1.5 1.5.69.72.72-.72 3.5-3.5.72-.72-1.44-1.41z" transform="translate(0 1)"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Registration requirements are satisfied.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_0488fb-cc"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-ic_check kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.41 0l-.69.72-2.78 2.78-.81-.78-.72-.72-1.41 1.41.72.72 1.5 1.5.69.72.72-.72 3.5-3.5.72-.72-1.44-1.41z" transform="translate(0 1)"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Documents become valid.</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_d85b61-f5"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-ic_check kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 8 8"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.41 0l-.69.72-2.78 2.78-.81-.78-.72-.72-1.41 1.41.72.72 1.5 1.5.69.72.72-.72 3.5-3.5.72-.72-1.44-1.41z" transform="translate(0 1)"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Certificates may become available for download.</span></li>
</ul></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For property registration cases, Approved generally means the registration process has been successfully completed.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column1845_beaa84-66"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading1845_1f359a-0c wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading1845_1f359a-0c"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">What Does Returned Status Mean?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Returned status means the application requires corrections before approval.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Common reasons include:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_f2cd13-97 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_1342ea-89"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_cornerDownRight kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 10 20 15 15 20"/><path d="M4 4v7a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h12"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Incorrect survey number</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_caf098-d1"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_cornerDownRight kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 10 20 15 15 20"/><path d="M4 4v7a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h12"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Missing documents</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_e65e88-cb"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_cornerDownRight kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 10 20 15 15 20"/><path d="M4 4v7a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h12"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Invalid information</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_95747d-22"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_cornerDownRight kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 10 20 15 15 20"/><path d="M4 4v7a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h12"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Signature mismatch</span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-1845_4a88a2-42"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_cornerDownRight kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 10 20 15 15 20"/><path d="M4 4v7a4 4 0 0 0 4 4h12"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Incomplete application</span></li>
</ul></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applicants should review the remarks provided and make the necessary corrections.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column1845_df1c25-da"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading1845_636a25-27 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading1845_636a25-27"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">What Does Rejected Status Mean?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Rejected status means the application cannot proceed.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Possible reasons include:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items1845_a51d37-b1 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
